  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\nAfter setting XXL text size from Appearance settings, the red warning background from Backup seed phrase popup is not resized based on the new text size\r\n<!-- Provide a short description describing the problem you are experiencing. -->\r\n<img width=\"1512\" alt=\"Screenshot 2022-11-23 at 12 06 44\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/47811206/203520687-4c731299-883c-4825-943c-c90a4675c1a1.png\">\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Go to Settings -> Appearance\r\n2. Set font size to XXL\r\n3. Go to Settings -> Back up seed phrase\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe textbox with red background should be resized to cover the new text size\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe textbox with red background is not resized and the text is overflowing\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version:\r\n- Operating System: MacOs\r\n\r\n",
